police said. He had been beaten with a blunt object and strangled, authorities 
said. 
</P>
<P>
Connelly was arrested three days later while driving Miranda's car in 
Hollywood, police said. 
</P>
<P>
Connelly, who had been living in California about three months at the time of 
the killing, had a history of mental illness, which was first discovered when 
he was 5, court documents said. 
