view from O'Halloran's porch at the Treasure Island park. ; Photo, Michael 
Kennedy, 42, and his fiancee, Sally Stanton, 39, enjoy the ocean vista from the 
porch of Kennedy's mobile home. KARI RENE HALL / Los Angeles Times; Photo, 
