The July 27 profile of the Willard Park section of Santa Ana included a picture 
of a building identified as new apartments. In fact, the building, French Park 
Place, designed by ML Partners, is the home of the 4th District Court of Appeal 
and is a winner of the prestigious Gold Nugget, an architecture award. 
</P>
